<P>AMERICA: OR, A POEM ON THE SETTLEMENT OF THE BRITISH COLONIES; ADDRESSED To the Friends of Freedom, and their Country.</P>
<P>By a <HI>GENTLEMAN</HI> educated at Yale-College.</P>
<P>NEW-HAVEN: Printed by THOMAS and SAMUEL GREEN.</P>
